FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775585464
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FThe youth centres will help young
OL,7,Fpeople aged up to 18 with employment
OL,8,Fadvice, health and wellbeing, and are
OL,9,Falso aimed at preventing them from
OL,10,Ffalling into a life of crime.
OL,12,FAreas of high anti-social behaviour
OL,13,Fhave been targeted for the first wave
OL,14,Fof the hubs, but they will be among 50
OL,15,Fwhich will open across the country.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
