FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775585464
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said:
OL,7,F"The closure of over a thousand youth
OL,8,Fcentres since 2010 didn't just take
OL,9,Faway facilities, it took away
OL,10,Fcommunity, connection and opportunity
OL,11,Ffor a generation. We are determined to
OL,12,Frebuild that.
OL,14,F"These hubs are about more than bricks
OL,15,Fand mortar, they're a statement that
OL,16,Fthis Government believes in young
OL,17,Fpeople and is investing in their
OL,18,Ffutures.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775585464
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"What makes them different is that
OL,7,Fwe're joining things up ` wellbeing
OL,8,Fsupport, crime prevention, work
OL,9,Fcoaches, youth services, all in one
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,F"We're making sure teenagers have
OL,13,Fsomewhere to go, someone to talk to
OL,14,Fand a real chance to thrive."
OL,16,FYoung people aged between 10 and 18,
OL,17,Fas well as those with special
OL,18,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,19,F(Send) up to the age of 25, will be
OL,20,Fable to access services at the youth
OL,21,Fcentres.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
