CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775585464
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FThe drive to open new youth hubs comes
OL,7,Famid a Government crackdown on knife
OL,8,Fcrime due to launch this week.
OL,10,FMinisters are hoping to halve knife
OL,11,Fcrime over the course of a decade as
OL,12,Fpart of a plan called Protecting
OL,13,FLives, Building Hope.
OL,15,FSarah Jones, the policing minister,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Knife crime devastates lives.
OL,18,F"Behind every statistic is a child who
OL,19,Fdidn't make it home, a family whose
OL,20,Fworld has been shattered, and a
OL,21,Fcommunity left with fear.
OL,26,@xD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
