FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775585464
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"This Government will halve knife
OL,7,Fcrime within a decade, saving lives
OL,8,Fand protecting communities.
OL,10,F"We will roll out young futures hubs
OL,11,Fin crime hotspots across the country
OL,12,Fto divert young people from violence,
OL,13,Fcut crime and protect communities."
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
